ide.frontend.classes

Class IDEPanelData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ide.frontend.classes.IDEPanelData

  • public class IDEPanelData
extends java.lang.Object
    Data Class being used by the IDEPanel class to store information concering wires between inputEvent and handlers. This class was created to clean the ide panel Class from this polution. This class also checks if a wire is being clicked.
    Author:
    Matthijs Kaminski
